    			<article id="post-3172" class="post-3172 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry">
				<div class="entry-content">
					<div class="row"><div class="column one-third"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-21239 size-full" src="https://www.iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Audur-osp-1.png" alt="" width="360" height="240" srcset="https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Audur-osp-1.png 360w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Audur-osp-1-300x200.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" /></p>
<p><strong>I heart Reykjavík</strong> is a <strong>one person travel guide</strong> dedicated to helping you realize<strong> Iceland is awesome</strong> &#8211; one post at a time!  I now also have an awesome travel company dedicated to making your stay in Reykjavík the best it can be.</p></div>
<div class="column one-third"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-21246 size-full" title="I live in Reykjavík" src="https://www.iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/reykjavik-1-copy.png" alt="" width="360" height="241" srcset="https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/reykjavik-1-copy.png 360w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/reykjavik-1-copy-300x201.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" /></p>
<p><strong>Don&#8217;t let the size of Reykjavík fool you</strong>, it&#8217;s got everything you will ever need and then some. My aim is to give you <strong>good honest advice about what Reykjavík has to offer,</strong> hopefully delivered in at least semi-entertaining way.</p></div>
<div class="column one-third last"><p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-21242 size-full" title="I love Iceland" src="https://www.iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Iceland2-1-copy.png" alt="" width="360" height="241" srcset="https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Iceland2-1-copy.png 360w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Iceland2-1-copy-300x201.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" /></p>
<p>Although Reykjavík is my first love <strong>you can&#8217;t visit Iceland without seeing some of our amazing natural wonders</strong>. Waterfalls, geysers, Northern Lights and quirky people &#8211; <strong>Iceland has it all.                                                                                                                  </strong></p></div><div class="clear"></div></div>
<div class="hr hr"></div>
<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-23386 size-full" src="https://www.iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scientist.png" width="930" height="81" srcset="https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scientist.png 930w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scientist-300x26.png 300w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scientist-768x67.png 768w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scientist-500x44.png 500w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scientist-800x70.png 800w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scientist-640x56.png 640w, https://iheartreykjavik.net/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Scientist-370x32.png 370w" sizes="(max-width: 930px) 100vw, 930px" /></p>
<div class="hr hr"></div>
